item.description: score:1153 Chances: Block reported second-quarter earnings that topped estimates, signaling a strong quarter for its consumer Cash App business. Square stock bulls focus on the potential synergies between Square’s Cash App and Afterpay, which could drive growth. The addition of Neha Narula, Director of the Digital Currency Initiative at the MIT Media Lab, to Block’s Board of Directors might bring valuable insights.
